umerical illustrations demonstrate the impact of energy\nharvesting on the achievable rate performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 09:53:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 6 Nov 2017 17:30:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-07"}
