 models may hint at a\nsolution to an observed discrepancy between the luminosity distribution\nfunctions of massive young stellar objects and compact HII regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 15:55:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
